
;アイテム説明と購入数
;ARG→選択項目
@ITEM_DETAIL_INSTITUTE(ARG)

;対応IDでないなら汎用出して帰る
;ここでは選択項目による
IF ARG < 10 || ARG > 10 +INSTITUTE_LIST_NUM
	PRINTL  　《 Item Decription Displayed Here 》
	RETURN
ENDIF

SELECTCASE ARG
CASE 10
	PRINTFORML Convert To Contribution Points：　Owned：%VALUE_DIGIT(MONEY:貢献PT)%pt
	PRINTFORML Rate：{EP_CONTRIBUTION_PT}EP→1 Contribution Point
	PRINTL
	PRINTL You can obtain ＜Contribution Points＞ by giving your stored spiritual power for research.

CASE 11
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("奴隷候補設定変更チケット")%＞　Owned：{ITEM:奴隷候補設定変更チケット} sheets
	PRINTFORML Required Spirit Energy：%VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:奴隷候補設定変更チケット)%EP
	PRINTL
	PRINTL You can exchange a mysterious ticket to change the tendencies of humans living on the surface.
	PRINTL However, it requires a large amount of stored spirit energy.
	IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
		PRINTL
		PRINTL To be honest, no one at the lab, including Eugene, understands how it works.
		PRINTL From a meta perspective, it's hard to integrate this concept into the world setting.
	ENDIF

CASE 12
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("霊力抽出装置")%＞　Owned: {ITEM:霊力抽出装置} units
	PRINTFORML 　Spirit Energy: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:霊力抽出装置 /2)%EP
	PRINTFORML 　        Funds: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:霊力抽出装置)%G
	PRINTL
	PRINTL With an additional extractor, you can perform simultaneous extraction on one more slave.

CASE 13
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("魔力枷")%＞　Owned: {ITEM:魔力枷} units
	PRINTFORML 　         Mana: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:魔力枷 /2)%MP
	PRINTFORML 　        Funds: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:魔力枷)%G
	PRINTL
	PRINTL Adds one Mana Shackles, increasing the number of non-subjugated slaves you can manage.

CASE 14
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("魔力補給装置")%＞
	PRINTFORML 　Spirit Energy: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:魔力補給装置)%EP
	PRINTFORML 　        Funds: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:魔力補給装置)%G
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A device for infusing stored Mana into living beings.
	PRINTFORML Allows %CALLNAME:0% to replenish Mana from the Mana reservoir.
	PRINTL Note: The maximum Mana does not increase during replenishment.
	PRINTL Available from the main menu under [Information] → [Ranch Info] → [Mana Replenishment].

CASE 15
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("魔改造魔力貯蔵器")%＞
	PRINTFORML 　Mana: %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_LARGE_CAPACITY)%MP
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("大容量魔力貯蔵器")%＞ required.
	PRINTL
	PRINTL Using the mana from a fully filled high-capacity mana storage, allows for further massive mana storage.
	IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
		PRINTL This is the result of everyone at the lab, including Eugene, having too much fun.
		PRINTL It's likely unnecessary to store this much mana.
	ENDIF

CASE 16
	PRINTFORML ＜%ITEMS_ENG("小型霊力抽出装置")%＞
	PRINTFORML 　        Funds: %VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:小型霊力抽出装置)%G
	PRINTL
	PRINTFORML This device attaches to a slave's %SAVESTR:表記／乳房% like a milking machine, extracting
	PRINTFORML %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% along with spirit energy.
	PRINTL It's compact and can be used during training sessions.
	IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
		PRINTL
		PRINTL Since it's provided at the start of the game, it's unlikely you'll need to create one.
	ENDIF
ENDSELECT


